comments.content: You can question her policies but you can’t question her integrity.
I can't agree with Ms. Chaney politically, but she has more integrity than most Republicans. I honor her for that.

As much as Liz and I disagree on many issues, I absolutely and wholeheartedly like her character as a person!!! She is a true patriot, and has the guts to actually take physical, clear steps, to shut down the circus. I knew about the ads she took in AZ for those races, and I applaud her walking the talk and backing her commitment to democracy and standing up against this fascist BS. Let’s be real, the message hit different when it’s coming from another Republican vs us progressives/dems. Liz, keep going! 🫡🇺🇸

In a time when I feel hopeless with respect to Americans and integrity, it is hopeful, that someone in the GOP lives in reality, and was willing to lose her congressional career to do what is right and to speak the truth. This is integrity.
I don't care for her politics but, she is the most courageous woman I have ever seen! I have immense respect for her!

I am a lifelong democrat... but I have the most profound respect for Liz Cheney... she has proven her integrity and loyalty to country over party in such a way as to be honored and celebrated. Best wishes to you Ms. Cheney
Perfect!  God Bless Liz for standing up to Donald Trump, something few Republicans have had the guts & courage to do.
She is amazing! If only there were more Republicans like her! She has guts, and never should have lost her seat. The people of her state are so stupid!!
A much bigger problem is our "Judicial" system that won't do a thing about him.

I think if Republicans were smart enough to back her, she'd become President. But they have so much pride they don't even realize they could implement their policies with her, and have the peaceful respect of the win from the rest of anybody else who has integrity, morals, ethics and more. We'd wish her well.
She nailed it
Keep going Liz! Good Americans respect you immensely.
Even though I’m not a Republican, I admire her for speaking up and fighting for truth in her own party.
Amazing ad. I never thought I would agree with Liz Cheney, but she is awesome! I hope she does lots of the ads!
Thank you Liz Cheney for your honesty! Keep doing what your doing!❤

Liz Cheney is incredibly courageous and has my utmost respect for her honesty and overall integration!!   Why did she have 2 stand so alone when there are so many Republicans who should have cared about America ?     Adam Kinsinger also stood against the horrific insurrection of Jan. 6th.  I admire his courage and honesty also.   Thank u Liz Cheney !!!
Honest and brave , the way we expect our elected officials to be. Thanks
I like this lady more and more
This ad should be shown around the entire country and played over and over again.
I have nothing but respect for Liz Chaney. She should be applauded.
